text: Liadagmis Povea Rodríguez (born 6 February 1996) is a Cuban athlete who specialises in the triple jump. She has qualified for 2016 Summer Olympics. In 2014, she won silver medal at the World Junior Championships. == Personal bests == === Outdoor === {| class="wikitable" |- ! Event !! Record !! Wind !! Venue !!
